sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Poll Official
    participant App as Official App
    participant Server as API Server
    participant DB as Database

    User->>App: Enter username and password
    App->>Server: Send encrypted login request
    Server->>DB: Validate credentials
    DB-->>Server: Valid or invalid

    alt Invalid credentials
        Server-->>App: Login failed (401)
        App-->>User: Show error message
    else Valid credentials
        Server-->>App: JWT token + profile (200)
        App-->>User: Login successful
    end
